{"tid":2517702,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[史詩級狀舉]公開自己連登名","createTime":"2021-05-05T13:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T13:08:56.000Z","uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"389052209246190946e20ddc7d364165cd22b07c","tid":2517702,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"相信對於大部分連登仔而言<br />\n連登名一直係佢哋最不可告人嘅秘密之一<br />\n就算係至親嘅人，都要對佢哋保密<br />\n只有極少數人夠膽同身邊至親嘅人講自己連登名<br />\n而會主動俾啲唔太熟嘅人知自己連登名嘅人<br />\n可以話根本一個都冇<br />\n甚至出現過因為俾朋友知道咗連登名<br />\n於是殺人滅口嘅事件<br />\n<strong>而今日<br />\n我決定完成一項狀舉</strong><br />\n大家連對住身邊嘅人都唔敢講嘅連登名<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">我決定<br />\n要喺全港最大嘅討論區-連登<br />\n向全香港公開自己嘅連登名</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">我嘅連登名就係</span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>戰鬥員D(加奈)！！！</strong></span><br />\n任何一個香港人<br />\n甚至係全世界<br />\n都可以睇到呢個post<br />\n換言之<br />\n我啱啱係向全世界公開咗自己最大嘅秘密<br />\n大家又有冇咁嘅勇氣？<br />\n如果冇，而又對我感到佩服嘅<br />\n麻煩請正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b5aa570203a1b0c571c7fada61a22794aa4a05","tid":2517702,"uid":335664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"dee2c2a91f784cf0471cfd2f8e99c3efc7b27b3e","tid":2517702,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6b5aa570203a1b0c571c7fada61a22794aa4a05","tid":2517702,"uid":335664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"閱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"正皮咗未？"},{"pid":"932474c5c5645f34203e7cb934a55ed9baccaed1","tid":2517702,"uid":21526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"Jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2d71c74a1cbdbc619c3a2d538d5e65b222e45c","tid":251